metadata.name: Block Quest PassKey
metadata.description:
This Block Quest PassKey allows entry to the token gated "Area 25" of Flagship

Add this NFT in your wallet connected to your Spatial.io account.

To find the entrance to Flagship Area-25, follow the clues below...

Time to leave the third dimension and build a foundation of knowledge.

This key is a single frame from one which exists in motion.

When you find it, look for three numbers with a single dot separating two

Remember this number

Go to the creator's page and see what is owned by them

Use the number to find an eye-catching piece

This creator has a number to see. But it's the first that makes an impression.

They will take you to many. This page is a resource. 

When required, it holds more value than just what is displayed.

The three plus one. hungry and focussed. 

In the centre, the two eyes colored to give you an advantage. 

There are always parts that will play a part, should you choose to continue.

If you do, you can expect more difficulty between the remaining passkeys.

But here's some information of value. 

You're half way home. 

To continue, head back to Flagship Gallery. If you are in the right place, then the location is clear. One of Two is with you. Where two are united, another clue awaits you.
